sentences: Assif Tsahar (born Israel, June 11, 1969) is an Israeli tenor saxophonist and bass clarinetist.
He has lived in New York City since 1990.
He founded the label Hopscotch Records in 1999.
In 2006 he opens the music club Levontin7 with Daniel Sarid in Tel Aviv.
